10. Security & Data Handling
* Input validation
* Schema verification
* Error handling for malformed data
* Controlled memory usage

11. Limitations
* Moving average does not handle seasonality
* No real-time live integration
* Static safety stock calculation
* Single-warehouse assumption

12. Future Enhancements
* LSTM-based demand forecasting
