* AI-driven anomaly detection
* Multi-agent supply chain simulation

13. Real-World Relevance
Modern supply chains at companies like:
* Amazon
* Walmart

use similar inventory optimization logic at scale.
This project simulates a simplified but realistic version of such systems.

14. Conclusion

The Agentic Warehouse Management System demonstrates:
* Applied Machine Learning
* Inventory Optimization Theory
* Agent-Based Decision Systems
* Data Engineering
* Supply Chain Intelligence

It bridges academic theory with real-world supply chain automation principles.
